definition: Hu county in Xi'an 西安[Xi1 an1], Shaanxi

sentences.english: Huxian farmer pictures are well known and there are lots of people who appreciate them.

sentences.english: Yang Weiming is a great farmer thinker in HU County, Shannxi province.

sentences.english: The history of the painting reflects a huge drop of times.
